= Games

== Object

[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`id` | `integer` |
|`owner` | `integer` |
|`center_point`  | `object` | lat/long. See example.
|`radius` | `float` | How far the boundary is from the center point in miles.
|`buy_in` | `float(string)` | How much it costs in BTC to join the game.
|`status` | `string` | Possible values: `pending`, `started`, `ended`.
|===

